OL,3,CPerrie Edwards reveals emotional toll
OL,4,Cof experiencing two miscarriages
OL,6,FFormer Little Mix star Perrie Edwards
OL,7,Fhas opened up about the emotional and
OL,8,Fphysical toll of her two miscarriages,
OL,9,Fcalling it "traumatic".
OL,11,FThe singer, 32, has two children with
OL,12,Ffootballer Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain,
OL,13,Fhowever, in a new emotional interview
OL,14,Fshe revealed the impact of previously
OL,15,Flosing two babies.
OL,17,FDuring her first pregnancy with Oxlade-
OL,18,FChamberlain, Edwards was told she had
OL,19,Fmiscarried at her first scan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
