OL,3,CPerrie Edwards reveals emotional toll
OL,4,Cof experiencing two miscarriages
OL,6,F"I just felt weird," she told Jamie
OL,7,FLaing on the Great Company podcast.
OL,9,F"It freaked me out moving forward and
OL,10,Fwhen I fell pregnant with Axel, the
OL,11,Fwhole pregnancy I was thinking 'oh no,
OL,12,Fthis could happen again.'
OL,14,F"So I felt scared to get attached, but
OL,15,Fthen I was attached and it was almost
OL,16,Fscary."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
