OL,3,CPerrie Edwards reveals emotional toll
OL,4,Cof experiencing two miscarriages
OL,6,FThe singer, who rose to fame after
OL,7,Fwinning the X Factor in 2011 alongside
OL,8,Fbandmates Jade Thirlwall, Jesy Nelson
OL,9,Fand Leigh-Anne Pinnock, gave birth to
OL,10,Fher son Axel in 2011.
OL,12,FThen, after falling pregnant again,
OL,13,Fshe and Oxlade-Chamberlain lost
OL,14,Fanother child at 24 weeks.
OL,16,F"We'd named him," Edwards said. "But
OL,17,Fbecause we'd just had Axel... I wasn't
OL,18,Feven thinking anything was going to go
OL,19,Fwrong until it went wrong and that was
OL,20,Ftraumatic."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
