PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781121969
OL,3,CPerrie Edwards reveals emotional toll
OL,4,Cof experiencing two miscarriages
OL,6,FBreaking down in tears, she said,
OL,7,F"Having to give birth to a child you
OL,8,Fcan't take home... It's awful."
OL,10,FDespite wanting more children, Edwards
OL,11,Fadmitted: "It took me a while to want
OL,12,Fto go again. But I just didn't have it
OL,13,Fin me. I was just terrified."
OL,15,FIn January 2026, the pair welcomed
OL,16,Ftheir daughter, Alanis Valentine,
OL,17,Fafter months of worrying whether the
OL,18,Fbaby would be okay.
OL,20,F"I was just on edge the whole time,"
OL,21,FEdwards said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
