OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781121969
OL,3,CPerrie Edwards reveals emotional toll
OL,4,Cof experiencing two miscarriages
OL,6,FThe singer said Oxlade-Chamberlain,
OL,7,Fwho she she has been engaged to since
OL,8,F2022, had "put on a brave face" but
OL,9,Fthat "he was struggling" too.
OL,11,FReflecting on the relationship, she
OL,12,Ftold Laing she thinks it is an example
OL,13,Fof "healthy love", and said: "I just
OL,14,Flove how calm he is and how
OL,15,Funderstanding he is and how caring he
OL,16,Fis and thoughtful he is.
OL,18,F"I just feel safe with Alex. I feel
OL,19,Fjust content and happy and it's not
OL,20,Feffort."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
